Add sieved @Flour{125%g}.
Add @Salt{1/2%teaspoon}.
Add @Baking Powder{2%teaspoon}.
Add @Sugar{1%tablespoon}.
Mix dry ingredients.
Add @Egg{1}.
Add @Milk{175%ml}.
Add cold melted @Butter{38%g}.
Add half teaspoon @Vanilla Essence{1/2%teaspoon}.
Make a well in flour and pour wet ingredients inside.
Stir with no lumps.
Cook with waffle machine.
